#: ../../postinstall.rst:371
msgid ""
"This screen is used to create the primary user account used to login to the "
"system. Create a strong password as the password is used whenever the system"
" indicates administrative access is required."
msgstr ""

#: ../../postinstall.rst:385
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`User Details` tab is used to create a login user. This screen"
" requires completing several fields:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../postinstall.rst:388
msgid ""
"**Name:** This value displays in the login screen. It can be the user's full"
" name and can contain both capital letters and spaces."
msgstr ""

#: ../../postinstall.rst:391
msgid ""
"**Username:** This is the name used when logging in. It can **not** contain "
"spaces and **is** case sensitive (e.g. *Kris* is a different username from "
"*kris*)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../postinstall.rst:395
msgid ""
"**Password:** This is the password to use when logging in. It must be typed "
"twice to confirm it."
msgstr ""

#: ../../postinstall.rst:398
msgid ""
"**Specify UID:** By default, the user will be assigned the next available "
"User ID (UID). If a specific UID is required, it can be set here."
msgstr ""

#: ../../postinstall.rst:402
msgid ""
"A UID can not be set lower than 1001, and a UID already in use by another "
"account will also be unavailable."
msgstr ""

#: ../../postinstall.rst:414
msgid ""
"When a user is configured to use a PersonaCrypt device, that user can not "
"login using an unencrypted session on the same system. In other words, the "
"PersonaCrypt username is reserved for PersonaCrypt use. If necessary to "
"login to both encrypted and unencrypted sessions on the same system, create "
"two different user accounts; one for each type of session."
msgstr ""

#: ../../postinstall.rst:436
msgid ""
"Check :guilabel:`Initialize PersonaCrypt Device`, insert a removable media "
"large enough to hold the files to store in the home directory, and click "
":guilabel:`Select`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../postinstall.rst:440
msgid ""
"Ensure there are no desired files on the removable media. Initializing the "
"media for PersonaCrypt will format the device with ZFS and encrypt it with "
"GELI, deleting any existing data."
msgstr ""

#: ../../postinstall.rst:448
msgid ""
"To share the computer with other users, create additional login and "
":ref:`PersonaCrypt` accounts using :ref:`User Manager`. After creating at "
"least one user, click :guilabel:`Next` to continue to the next screen."
msgstr ""

