#: ../../postinstall.rst:405
msgid ""
"|trueos| provides the ability to use a removable device, such as a USB "
"stick, as the user's encrypted home directory. This is useful in a multi-"
"user or multi-computer environment, as it provides the user with secure "
"access to their encrypted files.  When a user is configured to use "
":ref:`PersonaCrypt`, their username will only appear in the login menu if "
"the removable media associated with that |trueos| system is inserted. They "
"must input the password associated with the removable device in order to "
"login."
msgstr ""

#: ../../postinstall.rst:421
