#: ../../postinstall.rst:532
msgid ""
"If :guilabel:`Enable SSH` is checked, the SSH service will start and be "
"configured to start whenever the system boots. It also creates the firewall "
"rules needed to allow incoming SSH connections to the |trueos| system."
msgstr ""

#: ../../postinstall.rst:572
msgid ""
"**user:** Upon first login, the created **username** (from :ref:`Create a "
"User Screen`) is the only available login user. If additional users are "
"created using :ref:`User Manager`, they will be added to the drop-down menu "
"for more login choices. PCDM will not allow logging in as the *root* user. "
"Instead, whenever a utility requires administrative access, |trueos| will "
"first ask for the password of the login account."
